      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks these are good. but some of the wording feels a bit heavy/political? like \"empowered and seen\" or \"honors every person.\" can u give me some options that are a bit more neutral/business-like? i don't want to alienate any customers who might have different views on these things, i just want to say we're a welcoming place for everyone.",
